\n  operationProfiling:\n    mode: slowOp\n    slowOpThresholdMs: 200\n\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n8. SUMMARY OF NON-DEFAULT SETTINGS\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nSetting                               Observed Value                  MongoDB Default\n-------------------------------------+-------------------------------+------------------\nstorage.wiredTiger.journalCompressor  zlib                            snappy\nsystemLog.verbosity                   1                               0\noperationProfiling.slowOpThresholdMs  200 ms                          100 ms\nsecurity.authorization                enabled                         disabled\nsecurity.keyFile                      /etc/mongo-keyfile/keyfile      (none)\n\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nEND OF AUDIT -- NO CHANGES WERE MADE TO THE CLUSTER\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d0b9ccc0-abe8-4d54-847e-7fc1fa2a27a2","uuid":"7a2c47bb-0a85-4135-8aff-004a6fe6fc4d","timestamp":"2026-06-25T14:03:53.811Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"MongoDB Replica Set Compliance Audit\n=====================================\nAudit Date: 2026-06-25\nNamespace:  mongodb\nAuditor:    read-only inspection (no cluster mutations performed)\n\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n1. REPLICA SET OVERVIEW\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nReplica Set Name : mongodb-replica\nMember Count     : 3\nPrimary          : mongodb-replica-0.mongodb-replica-svc.mongodb.svc.cluster.local:27017\nSecondaries      : mongodb-replica-1.mongodb-replica-svc.mongodb.svc.cluster.local:27017\n                   mongodb-replica-2.mongodb-replica-svc.mongodb.svc.cluster.local:27017\nAll Members      : health=1 (U